    const m=monday(dateFrom(selected)),today=dateKey();$('#weekStrip').innerHTML=[0,1,2,3,4,5,6].map(i=>{const d=addDays(m,i),k=dateKey(d),w=workout(k);return`<button class="day-button ${k===selected?'active':''} ${w?'workout-day':''} ${state.workouts[k]?.complete?'complete':''}" data-date="${k}"><span>${d.toLocaleDateString(undefined,{weekday:'narrow'})}</span><b>${d.getDate()}</b></button>`}).join('');
